Package com.Game.model

Class Territory

java.lang.Object
com.Game.model.Territory
public class Territory extends Object
Represents a territory in the game. A territory is associated with a continent, has a certain number of armies, and can have neighbors (other territories). It also keeps track of its owner, reserved armies, and whether it has been visited.
